#. html
#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/distributed_search_instance.xml:171
msgid "<p>Health Condition indicates the overall status of the peer over the last 10 minutes.</p><p>Peer response times shown are computed over the last 10 minutes. Abnormally high response times (greater than 1000 ms) indicate peer oversubscription. <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.dmc.peerauth\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Splunk help\">Learn More</a></p><p><b>Authentication:</b> the search head requests an authentication token from the peer's /services/admin/auth-tokens endpoint. </p><p><b>Get Bundle List:</b> the search head requests a list of available knowledge bundles from the peer's /services/admin/bundles endpoint. </p><p><b>Get Peer Info:</b> the search head requests instance information from the peer's /services/server/info endpoint. </p>"
msgstr "<p>运行状况指示过去 10 分钟内节点的整体状态。</p><p>显示的节点响应时间基于过去 10 分钟计算得出。异常高的响应时间(大于 1000 毫秒)表示节点过度订阅。<a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.dmc.peerauth\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Splunk help\">了解更多信息</a></p><p><b>验证: </b>搜索头从节点的 /services/admin/auth-tokens 端点请求验证标记。</p><p><b>获取软件包列表: </b>搜索头从节点的 /services/admin/bundles 端点获取可用知识软件包列表。</p><p><b>获取节点信息: </b>搜索头从节点的 /services/server/info 端点请求实例信息。</p>"

